oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Joe Kerr Walker
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Edwin Best
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Greenback (Tenn.); Walker, Joe Kerr;
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Young boy on pony, holding on to horn of saddle. Feet do not reach the stirrups. Small colt next to pony. In a grassy field with a fence and buildings in the background. Woman is barely visible on right side of photograph. Harris Kerr Walker is written on back of photo.
